You know I was thinking about the political situation we’re in right now.
Nation representatives arguing and fighting are putting us one against each other.
But let’s face it we’ve been manipulated since the beginning of times, if our politicians fight then we start to hate, and that is not right. 
That is not us. That is not what we want to be. I love each and everyone of you my friends from wherever you are, every nation every country every island or piece of land on hearth. We’re all one big family, and we need to stand together to fight this. ♥️ Please share and let the world people 
feel united as one. 
God bless u
Mdv

WE NEED YOUR HELP TOO.🇮🇹🙏🏽 Please friends all over the world, I know a lot of you were asking me how to help and donate, I uploaded a lot of links in my stories, and also here with this tee you have another nice way to do it and a nice souvenir. 
Share please.

We love you, and we appreciate you. 
Team #Nohow ♥️ #iorestoacasa #andratuttobene #covid_19
